<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Seite nicht gefunden</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/images/TVG_Logo.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .error-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .error-content {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #003366;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #666;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .back-home {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: #d4af36;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .back-home:hover {
            background: #c29d28;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page">
        <div class="error-content">
            <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
            <p class="error-message">Oops! Diese Seite existiert nicht.</p>
            <p>Die gesuchte Seite konnte leider nicht gefunden werden.</p>
            <a href="/" class="back-home">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="white">
                    <path d="M20 11H7.83l5.59-5.59L12 4l-8 8 8 8 1.41-1.41L7.83 13H20v-2z"/>
